1) Sylvester "Syl" Rye ("Reed St. Claire" on paper) - protagonist.

2) Henry Kimo Mahoe, "Henry Jim", The Whispering Pines Roadhouse owner, Kanaka-heritage Hawaiian-American, former hermit, left the woods after a cryptid sighting (he adopted a lost child and then 6 years later found out the child is a very lethal cryprid), gentle personality like Sojiro from persona 5 ; his sister Auntie Nani Mahoe.

